# Swan Oyster Depot

* 1517 Polk St, San Francisco, CA 94109
* 415-673-1101
* Cash only

## Links

* https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swan_Oyster_Depot
* http://places.singleplatform.com/swan-oyster-depot/menu?ref=google
